The 21 year old me, who just started created content back then - could’ve never imagined that we’d be speaking at TEDx 6 years later! ❤️

Over this weekend - I got the chance to be a part of @tedxpodarworldcollege to speak about something SO close to my heart! Right from the pressure of being perfect to breaking free, this journey has been a rollercoaster of emotions - that I wouldn’t have in any other way! ✨

Consider this your sign to embrace who you are, have some faith, and take the leap! 🚀

Outfit @ashin.inn 💕

latestPosts.caption:
From seeing Indulekha in my mom’s cabinet…
to hand-making my own bottle of their new scalp serum —
this felt like a full-circle moment 🌿✨

@indulekha_care invited me to experience the making of their Bringha Scalp Serum — from plucking Ayurvedic herbs like Bringharaj, Amla, and Yashtimadhu, to crafting the Kashayam extract and assembling the bottle, step by step 💚

What stood out the most?
It’s clinically proven to grow 11,000+ new hairs — backed by Ayurvedic science and powered by nature 🧪🌱

Scalp analysis, ingredient education, and immersive zones made this more than just an event — it was a reminder that real care starts at the root.

Rooted in tradition. Proven by results.

#AD#Indulekha #BringhaScalpSerum #ClinicallyProven #11000NewHairs #AyurvedicCare #HairCareThatWorks #RootedInResults #SelfCareJourney
